<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - AC-Rush</title>
    <meta name="description" content="AC-Rush is a premium platform for competitive programming and DSA practice. Learn, grow, and prepare for technical interviews.">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header-content">
                <a href="/" class="logo">AC-Rush</a>
                <nav>
                    <a href="/">Problems</a>
                    <a href="/about">About</a>
                    <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
                    <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
                        <a href="/profile" class="nav-btn nav-btn-outline">Profile</a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <a href="/login" class="nav-btn nav-btn-outline">Log In</a>
                    <% } %>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="page-hero">
                <h1>About AC-Rush</h1>
                <p>A premium platform designed for those who want to master the art of problem solving</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-section">
                <h2>What We Do</h2>
                <p>
                    AC-Rush is a competitive programming and DSA practice platform built for serious learners. We provide carefully curated problems spanning arrays, trees, graphs, dynamic programming, and more — designed to progressively challenge and improve your skills.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Whether you're preparing for technical interviews at top companies, training for programming contests like ICPC and Codeforces, or simply looking to sharpen your problem-solving abilities — AC-Rush offers the focused environment you need.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-section">
                <h2>Our Purpose</h2>
                <div class="content-grid">
                    <div class="content-card">
                        <h3>Deliberate Learning</h3>
                        <p>Every problem is selected and categorized to help you build skills systematically. Progress from fundamentals to advanced algorithms at your own pace.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="content-card">
                        <h3>Contest Preparation</h3>
                        <p>Train with problems that mirror the difficulty and style of real competitive programming contests. Build speed and accuracy under pressure.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="content-card">
                        <h3>Interview Readiness</h3>
                        <p>Master the data structures and algorithms that top tech companies ask about. Build confidence through consistent, structured practice.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="content-card">
                        <h3>Growth Mindset</h3>
                        <p>Track your progress, challenge yourself with harder problems, and watch your problem-solving intuition develop over time.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content-section">
                <h2>Technology</h2>
                <p>
                    AC-Rush is built with modern web technologies and supports code execution in Python, C++, and Java. Our AI-powered hints and explanations help you learn from every problem, not just solve it.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 AC-Rush. Master algorithms, one problem at a time.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            const header = document.querySelector('header');
            if (header) header.classList.toggle('scrolled', window.scrollY > 10);
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
